01:04:41.336 --> 01:04:43.456
[male cultist] Send more people
to guard the entrance.

819
01:04:47.926 --> 01:04:49.928
[dramatic music playing]

820
01:05:12.867 --> 01:05:14.494
- [Maria] You good?
- Yeah.

821
01:05:14.577 --> 01:05:16.538
[Asia panting]

822
01:05:24.087 --> 01:05:25.463
- [grunts]
- [bullet ricochets]

823
01:05:32.303 --> 01:05:33.388
[gun clicking]

824
01:05:37.308 --> 01:05:39.060
- [Maria] Asia.
- Yes.

825
01:05:39.144 --> 01:05:40.854
[Maria] Come on! Shoot him!

826
01:05:42.564 --> 01:05:44.566
[air whooshing]

827
01:05:47.110 --> 01:05:48.111
[exhales]

828
01:05:49.154 --> 01:05:50.280
[grunts]

829
01:05:53.783 --> 01:05:54.784
[grunts]

830
01:05:57.745 --> 01:05:58.746
[yells]

831
01:06:05.211 --> 01:06:06.212
[Maria] Go!

832
01:06:08.173 --> 01:06:09.340
[grunts]

833
01:06:13.595 --> 01:06:15.430
Oh. my God! Oh. my God!

834
01:06:15.513 --> 01:06:16.514
[Maria yelling]

835
01:06:17.891 --> 01:06:19.017
[man yells]

836
01:06:26.774 --> 01:06:27.817
[Asia] Fuck!

837
01:06:27.901 --> 01:06:28.902
[grunts]

838
01:06:32.363 --> 01:06:33.364
[Lily] That's it.

839
01:06:34.741 --> 01:06:35.742
It's over.

840
01:06:35.825 --> 01:06:37.827
[suspenseful music playing]

841
01:06:41.623 --> 01:06:43.541
[thunder rumbling]

842
01:06:45.793 --> 01:06:46.836
No. it's not.

843
01:06:46.920 --> 01:06:48.171
You're ridiculous.

844
01:06:48.254 --> 01:06:50.089
[cultists laugh]

845
01:06:51.925 --> 01:06:53.801
You need me alive
for the sacrifice. don't you?

846
01:06:54.969 --> 01:06:56.137
Let Maria go.

847
01:06:56.221 --> 01:06:57.514
or I'll jump.

848
01:06:58.681 --> 01:07:01.226
- You can scrape up what's left.
- [Maria] Asia. no.

849
01:07:01.392 --> 01:07:02.644
So selfless.

850
01:07:03.520 --> 01:07:05.063
And so misguided.

851
01:07:06.397 --> 01:07:08.399
Do you even know whose life
you're fighting for?

852
01:07:09.234 --> 01:07:10.234
Lily. please.

853
01:07:10.276 --> 01:07:12.403
The fuck are you talking about?

854
01:07:13.571 --> 01:07:14.822
Didn't you ever think...

855
01:07:15.990 --> 01:07:18.785
How exactly did your dear sister

856
01:07:18.868 --> 01:07:22.121
come from being
just another one of our sacrifices

857
01:07:22.247 --> 01:07:25.792
to have a chance to join our family?

858
01:07:26.417 --> 01:07:29.546
What deal has she made?

859
01:07:36.135 --> 01:07:37.845
We'll take care of you.

860
01:07:38.471 --> 01:07:39.847
Do you understand?

861
01:07:40.974 --> 01:07:42.100
[Maria] Yes.

862
01:07:42.183 --> 01:07:43.393
Splendid.

863
01:07:44.269 --> 01:07:46.688
You will pledge to our Lord.

864
01:07:46.771 --> 01:07:51.192
When the time comes.
you will put your name on the list.

865
01:07:51.734 --> 01:07:54.571
Then you seal the deal with blood.

866
01:07:55.488 --> 01:07:57.156
You kill your sacrifice. dear.

867
01:07:59.033 --> 01:08:01.035
One death for one life.

868
01:08:01.160 --> 01:08:03.913
A small price for immortality.

869
01:08:04.747 --> 01:08:10.295
But if you break your word. run away.
or don't find an offering

870
01:08:12.338 --> 01:08:14.090
our Lord will take you.

871
01:08:14.173 --> 01:08:15.800
[dramatic music playing]

872
01:08:18.803 --> 01:08:20.283
[Maria] <i>I didn't want to hurt anyone.</i>

873
01:08:22.015 --> 01:08:23.600
<i>But there was no way out of this deal.</i>

874
01:08:25.101 --> 01:08:26.894
<i>I committed my soul to the Devil.</i>

875
01:08:28.896 --> 01:08:30.565
<i>Isabelle Davison.</i>

876
01:08:30.648 --> 01:08:33.943
<i>a woman from my last job.
was supposed to be my sacrifice.</i>

877
01:08:35.820 --> 01:08:36.880
Oh. it's a small tradition.

878
01:08:36.904 --> 01:08:38.781
[Maria] <i>But instead. you showed up.</i>

879
01:08:38.906 --> 01:08:42.076
[Lily] One of our maids will be
rewarded tonight for her dedication.

880
01:08:42.201 --> 01:08:43.953
[Maria] <i>And now. I'm out of time.</i>

881
01:08:45.079 --> 01:08:46.372
[glasses clink]

882
01:08:46.456 --> 01:08:48.041
To Isabelle's memory.

883
01:08:48.124 --> 01:08:49.459
[all] To Isabelle.

884
01:08:49.542 --> 01:08:51.377
<i>- Salud.
- Salud.</i>

885
01:08:51.461 --> 01:08:53.129
[Maria] <i>Without a sacrifice tonight...</i>

886
01:08:54.797 --> 01:08:56.049
[swallows. exhales]

887
01:08:56.132 --> 01:08:57.258
<i>I'm dead.</i>

888
01:09:08.227 --> 01:09:10.313
I feel sorry for you. Asia.

889
01:09:10.396 --> 01:09:11.522
Honestly.

890
01:09:12.231 --> 01:09:15.360
All this for nothing.

891
01:09:15.443 --> 01:09:16.527
Take them.

892
01:09:17.528 --> 01:09:19.030
- No. No. no. no.
- Come on. Move!

893
01:09:19.113 --> 01:09:21.407
No! No! No!

894
01:09:24.994 --> 01:09:26.996
[ethereal music playing]

895
01:09:39.175 --> 01:09:40.385
[Asia grunts]

896
01:09:48.851 --> 01:09:49.852
[snarls]

897
01:09:51.312 --> 01:09:52.855
[Asia whimpers]

898
01:09:58.403 --> 01:10:00.446
