910
01:11:32.288 --> 01:11:33.539
[Asia winces]

911
01:11:46.010 --> 01:11:47.553
[low growl]

912
01:12:02.276 --> 01:12:03.569
[low grunt]

913
01:12:27.134 --> 01:12:28.135
[snorts]

914
01:12:29.512 --> 01:12:31.514
