933
01:13:53.304 --> 01:13:56.724
[bellows]

934
01:14:04.148 --> 01:14:05.858
No. no. No.

935
01:14:18.037 --> 01:14:19.580
I can't let you go.

936
01:14:21.040 --> 01:14:22.333
I made my choice.

937
01:14:24.877 --> 01:14:26.504
Now it's your turn. darling.

938
01:14:30.174 --> 01:14:31.634
