939
01:14:31.759 --> 01:14:32.759
[Lily gasps]

940
01:14:33.427 --> 01:14:34.595
[The Head growls]

941
01:14:43.938 --> 01:14:44.939
[Kevin grunting]

942
01:14:49.485 --> 01:14:50.528
Now. girls.

943
01:14:50.653 --> 01:14:52.071
[blade clangs]

944
01:14:54.782 --> 01:14:56.200
[The Head] Maria

945
01:14:57.118 --> 01:14:59.328
your time has come.

946
