964
01:16:04.185 --> 01:16:05.185
[Asia's muffled grunts]

965
01:16:09.732 --> 01:16:11.609
I wish we had more time. [Exhales]

966
01:16:16.155 --> 01:16:17.865
This is the only way.

967
01:16:19.784 --> 01:16:21.577
- [blade slashes]
- [grunts]

968
01:16:29.460 --> 01:16:31.462
[somber music playing]

969
01:16:57.780 --> 01:17:01.200
I'm so sorry.

970
01:17:18.801 --> 01:17:19.969
[The Head growls]

971
01:17:20.094 --> 01:17:21.095
Is she dead?

972
