Looks pretty dead to me.

973
01:17:26.767 --> 01:17:27.935
[Asia grunts]

974
01:17:30.396 --> 01:17:32.398
[suspenseful music playing]

975
01:17:44.368 --> 01:17:48.080
One death for one life.

976
01:17:54.545 --> 01:17:55.713
[Asia yelling]

977
01:18:10.019 --> 01:18:13.480
[Lily] Maria sacrificed herself
to make Asia immortal!

978
01:18:14.315 --> 01:18:15.900
Holy fuck.

979
01:18:16.442 --> 01:18:17.568
[Lily exhales]

980
01:18:20.321 --> 01:18:21.572
[The Head growls]

981
01:18:24.158 --> 01:18:26.493
Get the skin! Erase her name!

982
01:18:27.453 --> 01:18:28.453
[grunts]

983
01:18:35.878 --> 01:18:36.921
Dude.

984
01:18:37.755 --> 01:18:38.755
[growls]

985
01:18:38.797 --> 01:18:40.466
[heavy rock music playing]

986
01:18:47.514 --> 01:18:48.766
- [choking]
- [Asia grunts]

987
01:18:59.777 --> 01:19:01.320
[Asia yells. exhales]

988
01:19:02.363 --> 01:19:03.447
[grunts]

989
01:19:04.823 --> 01:19:06.367
[groans in agony]

990
01:19:06.951 --> 01:19:07.951
[Asia yells]

991
01:19:09.787 --> 01:19:11.789
[both grunting]

992
01:19:16.919 --> 01:19:17.920
[Asia yells]

993
01:19:24.927 --> 01:19:25.927
[Sharon gasps]

994
01:19:33.978 --> 01:19:35.104
[gasps]

995
01:19:36.438 --> 01:19:37.690
[The Head growls]

996
01:19:40.401 --> 01:19:41.944
[Lily and Asia grunting]

997
01:19:43.821 --> 01:19:45.406
- [Bob grunts]
- [Asia yelps]

998
01:19:53.872 --> 01:19:56.000
Ha! Help me. my Lord.

999
01:19:58.252 --> 01:20:00.170
- [steam hisses]
- [Bob grunts]

1000
01:20:09.263 --> 01:20:10.264
[gasps]

1001
01:20:14.018 --> 01:20:15.853
[choking]

1002
01:20:18.689 --> 01:20:19.689
[exhales]

1003
01:20:27.740 --> 01:20:28.866
[The Head grunting]

1004
01:20:29.325 --> 01:20:30.451
[roars]

1005
01:20:32.036 --> 01:20:33.579
[screeching]

1006
01:20:41.754 --> 01:20:42.754
[screeches]

1007
01:20:46.592 --> 01:20:47.593
[growls]

1008
01:20:50.220 --> 01:20:51.597
[low growl]

1009
01:20:53.724 --> 01:20:56.518
You want to play with swords?

1010
01:20:56.643 --> 01:20:58.062
Let's play.

1011
01:20:59.313 --> 01:21:00.356
[roaring]

1012
01:21:02.024 --> 01:21:03.108
[yells]

1013
01:21:18.207 --> 01:21:19.249
[Asia yells]

1014
01:21:36.558 --> 01:21:38.102
[Asia yells]

1015
01:21:53.242 --> 01:21:54.952
[both grunting]

1016
01:22:01.583 --> 01:22:02.709
[Asia groans]

1017
01:22:08.006 --> 01:22:09.383
[The Head as Maria] Hey. Butthead.

1018
01:22:09.967 --> 01:22:11.385
you should have left me.

1019
01:22:12.010 --> 01:22:13.720
I'd still be alive.

1020
01:22:14.888 --> 01:22:17.015
I died because of you.

1021
01:22:19.393 --> 01:22:20.436
Leave

1022
01:22:21.728 --> 01:22:23.605
my sister

1023
01:22:25.315 --> 01:22:26.316
alone.

1024
01:22:26.400 --> 01:22:28.402
[intriguing music playing]

1025
01:22:33.740 --> 01:22:34.740
[snarls]

1026
01:22:41.290 --> 01:22:42.875
[yells]

1027
01:22:45.210 --> 01:22:46.795
[screeches]

1028
01:22:46.879 --> 01:22:48.338
[The Head squeals]

1029
01:22:50.299 --> 01:22:51.467
[Lily screams]

1030
01:22:54.219 --> 01:22:55.721
[scream echoes]

1031
01:23:00.893 --> 01:23:02.603
[flesh squelching]

1032
01:23:10.777 --> 01:23:11.945
[The Head snorts]

1033
01:23:16.074 --> 01:23:17.201
[snorts]

1034
01:23:17.326 --> 01:23:19.453
I want my sister back.

1035
01:23:19.536 --> 01:23:21.663
Of course you do.

1036
01:23:21.788 --> 01:23:23.457
You know the deal.

1037
01:23:23.540 --> 01:23:25.834
One death for one life.

1038
01:23:28.253 --> 01:23:30.255
I think we can do better than that.

1039
01:23:31.673 --> 01:23:32.966
[howls]

1040
01:23:35.552 --> 01:23:37.513
[grunts]

1041
01:23:40.224 --> 01:23:41.808
[coughs. splutters]

1042
01:23:42.768 --> 01:23:44.102
[cigarette lighter clicks]

1043
01:23:44.228 --> 01:23:45.229
Shit.

1044
01:23:46.563 --> 01:23:48.524
[roars in pain]

1045
01:23:52.778 --> 01:23:54.404
[rap song playing]

1046
01:23:57.407 --> 01:23:58.450
Just a flesh wound.

1047
01:24:05.082 --> 01:24:06.708
[chokes]

1048
01:24:08.293 --> 01:24:09.836
[grunts]

1049
01:24:12.422 --> 01:24:13.590
Oh. no.

1050
01:24:17.886 --> 01:24:19.429
[groans]

1051
01:24:28.146 --> 01:24:30.315
I'll see you

1052
01:24:30.899 --> 01:24:32.693
in hell...

1053
01:24:34.027 --> 01:24:35.904
Asia Reaves.

1054
01:24:37.114 --> 01:24:38.574
[The Head screaming]

1055
01:24:38.699 --> 01:24:40.576
I fucking hope so. bitch.

1056
01:24:43.620 --> 01:24:45.038
[screams echo]

1057
01:25:22.784 --> 01:25:25.787
If I were you. I'd clear out.

1058
01:25:27.331 --> 01:25:29.333
[dramatic music playing]

1059
01:25:37.924 --> 01:25:39.926
[dramatic music playing]

1060
01:25:45.390 --> 01:25:48.685
[Asia grunts. pants]

1061
01:25:48.810 --> 01:25:50.646
[alarm ringing]

1062
01:25:58.820 --> 01:26:00.113
[grunts]

1063
01:26:18.256 --> 01:26:19.424
What happened in there?

1064
01:26:20.425 --> 01:26:21.425
Rich people.

1065
01:26:24.805 --> 01:26:25.805
Hmm.

1066
01:26:26.682 --> 01:26:27.724
[Asia exhales]

1067
01:26:32.145 --> 01:26:33.145
[sighs]

1068
01:26:37.317 --> 01:26:40.028
Hey. I'm... I'm...

1069
01:26:40.153 --> 01:26:43.281
I'm just so sorry for your loss.

1070
01:26:44.700 --> 01:26:46.159
I could take you wherever you...

1071
01:26:47.619 --> 01:26:48.704
What is that?

1072
01:26:53.333 --> 01:26:54.918
What the fuck is that?

1073
01:26:55.043 --> 01:26:56.837
- [Maria gasps]
- Jesus Christ!

1074
01:26:56.920 --> 01:26:58.880
[Maria hyperventilates]

1075
01:27:01.717 --> 01:27:03.093
[exhales]

1076
01:27:03.176 --> 01:27:04.176
Maria.

1077
01:27:05.762 --> 01:27:07.522
- Asia.
- [private investigator] What the fuck?

1078
01:27:10.767 --> 01:27:11.768
What happened?

1079
01:27:12.227 --> 01:27:15.772
Well. that's a great question.
because you were just fuckin' dead!

1080
01:27:16.314 --> 01:27:17.899
[The Head groaning]

1081
01:27:18.900 --> 01:27:20.360
[Asia] <i>I changed my name to yours.</i>

1082
01:27:21.194 --> 01:27:22.904
<i>And I killed all those motherfuckers.</i>

1083
01:27:25.365 --> 01:27:27.784
What the hell are you two talking about?

1084
01:27:30.370 --> 01:27:31.747
[giggles]

1085
01:27:32.664 --> 01:27:33.665
I told you.

1086
01:27:34.374 --> 01:27:36.460
I'm never gonna leave you again.

1087
01:27:45.927 --> 01:27:46.928
[chuckles softly]

1088
01:27:50.807 --> 01:27:51.808
You know what?

1089
01:27:52.642 --> 01:27:53.643
I don't want to know.

1090
01:27:54.227 --> 01:27:55.645
Fuck it.

1091
01:27:56.229 --> 01:27:57.939
Fuck it! [Chuckles]

1092
01:28:03.278 --> 01:28:04.821
- [engine starts]
- Where we going?

1093
01:28:05.530 --> 01:28:07.115
